01:12:37,960 --> 01:12:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna osoba, majka sedmero djece,

2029
01:12:41,460 --> 01:12:43,399
[SPEAKER_00] dvoje djece posvojene,

2030
01:12:43,399 --> 01:12:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] djete sa davnovim sindromom,

2031
01:12:45,079 --> 01:12:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] autentični svjedok, karizmatik

2032
01:12:47,539 --> 01:12:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] i došla je tamo i ona je bila taj jezičac na vagi

2033
01:12:51,779 --> 01:12:53,260
[SPEAKER_00] da padne zakon o pobačaju.

2034
01:12:53,260 --> 01:12:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] Padne zakon o pobačaju.

2035
01:12:55,619 --> 01:12:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] 280 miliona ljudi, sad blizu 300 miliona većim u SAD-u.

2036
01:13:01,500 --> 01:13:09,800
[SPEAKER_00] To su nam primjeri i uzori koji nas moraju potaknuti šta znači imat širinu duha i dijelovat hrabro.

2037
01:13:11,979 --> 01:13:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ok?

2038
01:13:12,659 --> 01:13:16,319
[SPEAKER_00] Tri kralja su bili takva ekipa.

2039
01:13:16,319 --> 01:13:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna predaja

2040
01:13:17,619 --> 01:13:20,239
[SPEAKER_00] kaže čak da je

2041
01:13:20,239 --> 01:13:22,520
[SPEAKER_00] to i dosta autentično,

2042
01:13:22,520 --> 01:13:24,020
[SPEAKER_00] da ih je sveti Toma apostol,

2043
01:13:24,020 --> 01:13:25,500
[SPEAKER_00] pošto su živjeli u Perziji,

2044
01:13:25,500 --> 01:13:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] na putu do Indije susrao

2045
01:13:27,960 --> 01:13:29,260
[SPEAKER_00] i da ih je i krstio.

2046
01:13:29,260 --> 01:13:32,520
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, možemo reći da se stvarno radi o kršćanskim svecima

2047
01:13:32,520 --> 01:13:34,560
[SPEAKER_00] koji su i primili krštenje.

2048
01:13:34,640 --> 01:13:36,760
[SPEAKER_00] Di se pokazala njihova snaga?

2049
01:13:36,760 --> 01:13:37,939
[SPEAKER_00] Nisu se sablaznili.

2050
01:13:37,939 --> 01:13:41,220
[SPEAKER_00] Vidli su pismo znance koji su truli,

2051
01:13:41,220 --> 01:13:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] vidli su Heroda koji nije pravi kralj,

2052
01:13:43,420 --> 01:13:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] vidli su da

2053
01:13:44,539 --> 01:13:47,939
[SPEAKER_00] ih je njihova logika dovela na krivi trag,

2054
01:13:47,939 --> 01:13:49,359
[SPEAKER_00] ali oni i dalje traže.

2055
01:13:49,359 --> 01:13:51,260
[SPEAKER_00] I baš zato jer su bili revni,

2056
01:13:51,260 --> 01:13:53,180
[SPEAKER_00] jer nisu dopustili da ih sablazan

2057
01:13:53,180 --> 01:13:55,220
[SPEAKER_00] odvoji od potrge za Bogom,

2058
01:13:55,220 --> 01:13:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] a to ono što moramo od njih naučiti.

2059
01:13:57,340 --> 01:14:00,560
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mnogi ljudi koriste sablazne kao izliku.

2060
01:14:00,560 --> 01:14:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ne želim se mijenjati, pa ću reći

2061
01:14:03,199 --> 01:14:04,359
[SPEAKER_00] crkva je takva i takva,

2062
01:14:04,359 --> 01:14:06,220
[SPEAKER_00] ovi su svi ovakvi, šta ću ja tamo?

2063
01:14:06,220 --> 01:14:08,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, oni su i dalje tragali

2064
01:14:08,819 --> 01:14:10,060
[SPEAKER_00] i Bog ih je nagradio.

2065
01:14:10,060 --> 01:14:12,859
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, kad su išli od Heroda,

2066
01:14:12,859 --> 01:14:14,060
[SPEAKER_00] opet su ugledali zvijezdu

2067
01:14:14,060 --> 01:14:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže, kad ugledaš te zvijezdu,

2068
01:14:15,500 --> 01:14:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] obradovaš se se radošću veoma velikom.

2069
01:14:18,539 --> 01:14:20,600
[SPEAKER_00] Otvorenost duha,

2070
01:14:20,600 --> 01:14:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] vjernost unatoč sablaznima.

2071
01:14:23,880 --> 01:14:25,779
[SPEAKER_00] Kakav primjer za nas?

2072
01:14:25,779 --> 01:14:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] Često, isto vidim,

2073
01:14:36,039 --> 01:14:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] ako se bojimo ući u dialog

2074
01:14:37,619 --> 01:14:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] sa drugima

2075
01:14:39,920 --> 01:14:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] o svoj vjeri

2076
01:14:41,460 --> 01:14:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] i o svojom iskustvu,

2077
01:14:42,539 --> 01:14:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] to znači često da nismo dovoljno sigurni

2078
01:14:45,119 --> 01:14:46,439
[SPEAKER_00] ni u vlastiti identitet,

2079
01:14:46,439 --> 01:14:49,359
[SPEAKER_00] te ne smatramo sebe i svoje iskustvo vjere

2080
01:14:49,359 --> 01:14:51,020
[SPEAKER_00] dovoljno sigurnim

2081
01:14:51,020 --> 01:14:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] i zanimljivim.

2082
01:14:52,159 --> 01:14:54,079
[SPEAKER_00] I zbog tog se bojimo

2083
01:14:54,079 --> 01:14:55,520
[SPEAKER_00] ulaziti u dijaloge

2084
01:14:55,520 --> 01:14:57,100
[SPEAKER_00] i ostajemo zatvoreni.

2085
01:14:57,100 --> 01:15:01,319
[SPEAKER_00] Često gradimo svoj identitet

2086
01:15:01,319 --> 01:15:02,739
[SPEAKER_00] u suparništu s drugima.

2087
01:15:02,739 --> 01:15:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je danas veliki problem.

2088
01:15:04,000 --> 01:15:08,239
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mi ne znamo ko smo

2089
01:15:08,239 --> 01:15:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] ako nismo u sukobu s drugima.

2090
01:15:10,000 --> 01:15:12,640
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ne volimo Dinamo

2091
01:15:12,640 --> 01:15:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] dok se ne pojavi Hajduk.

2092
01:15:13,840 --> 01:15:14,840
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se pojavi Hajduk

2093
01:15:14,840 --> 01:15:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] i onda smo baš za Dinamo.

2094
01:15:16,039 --> 01:15:17,739
[SPEAKER_00] Znate kako to koriste,

2095
01:15:17,739 --> 01:15:18,899
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost, političari

2096
01:15:18,899 --> 01:15:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] u cijelom, u Hrvatskoj

2097
01:15:21,800 --> 01:15:22,720
[SPEAKER_00] više manje,

2098
01:15:22,720 --> 01:15:23,859
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo, pogledajte recimo

2099
01:15:23,859 --> 01:15:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] u Srbi ili u Bosni i Hercegovini.

2100
01:15:26,539 --> 01:15:28,779
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je ekonomija jako loše,

2101
01:15:28,779 --> 01:15:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] kad je nezaposlenost,

2102
01:15:30,579 --> 01:15:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi se isseljavaju,

2103
01:15:31,960 --> 01:15:33,399
[SPEAKER_00] e, šta onda?

2104
01:15:33,399 --> 01:15:34,979
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo sad pričati

2105
01:15:34,979 --> 01:15:36,119
[SPEAKER_00] o drugom svjetskom ratu,

2106
01:15:36,119 --> 01:15:36,739
[SPEAKER_00] o Ustašama,

2107
01:15:36,739 --> 01:15:37,680
[SPEAKER_00] o Partizanima,

2108
01:15:37,680 --> 01:15:38,600
[SPEAKER_00] o Jasenovcu,

2109
01:15:38,600 --> 01:15:39,319
[SPEAKER_00] Blajburgu,

2110
01:15:39,319 --> 01:15:40,479
[SPEAKER_00] o Srebrenici.

2111
01:15:40,479 --> 01:15:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto to rade?

2112
01:15:41,340 --> 01:15:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pa zato,

2113
01:15:43,500 --> 01:15:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] jel ti ljudi

2114
01:15:45,239 --> 01:15:46,720
[SPEAKER_00] svoj identitet grade

2115
01:15:46,720 --> 01:15:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] samo kontra nekog?

2116
01:15:48,899 --> 01:15:51,500
[SPEAKER_00] A ne iz onog šta ti jesi.

2117
01:15:51,500 --> 01:15:54,899
[SPEAKER_00] I postoji velika opasnost

2118
01:15:54,899 --> 01:15:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] da i crkva počne na taj način djelovati.

2119
01:15:57,619 --> 01:15:59,439
[SPEAKER_00] A vidjeli smo da se to dogodilo.

2120
01:15:59,439 --> 01:16:01,640
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo imali oporbu komunista,

2121
01:16:01,640 --> 01:16:03,680
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj pomazuje pet tisuća.

2122
01:16:03,680 --> 01:16:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je došla demokracija,

2123
01:16:05,800 --> 01:16:07,600
[SPEAKER_00] mogu svi svećenici sad ići.

2124
01:16:07,600 --> 01:16:09,020
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo ovaj lud ko ide

2125
01:16:09,020 --> 01:16:10,600
[SPEAKER_00] tamo sa biciklom.

2126
01:16:11,760 --> 01:16:12,760
[SPEAKER_00] nego svi mogu doći.

2127
01:16:12,760 --> 01:16:13,520
[SPEAKER_00] Nema nikog.

2128
01:16:13,520 --> 01:16:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

2129
01:16:14,960 --> 01:16:16,319
[SPEAKER_00] Zato li je trulo iznutra?

2130
01:16:16,319 --> 01:16:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo svjesni svog identiteta.

2131
01:16:18,260 --> 01:16:21,180
[SPEAKER_00] Dijelujemo samo iz oporbe

2132
01:16:21,180 --> 01:16:22,020
[SPEAKER_00] prema drugima.

2133
01:16:22,020 --> 01:16:25,060
[SPEAKER_00] Češki teolog Tomas Halik

2134
01:16:25,060 --> 01:16:26,359
[SPEAKER_00] je...

2135
01:16:26,359 --> 01:16:30,399
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo ovo smatra

2136
01:16:30,399 --> 01:16:32,520
[SPEAKER_00] najvećim problemom crkve danas.

2137
01:16:32,520 --> 01:16:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže ovako.

2138
01:16:33,720 --> 01:16:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, u Češkoj

2139
01:16:35,000 --> 01:16:37,260
[SPEAKER_00] je oporbu protiv komunizma

2140
01:16:37,260 --> 01:16:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] i izlazak iz Čeho-Slovačke

2141
01:16:39,420 --> 01:16:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] su vodili vjernici.

2142
01:16:40,880 --> 01:16:42,140
[SPEAKER_00] Danas je Češka

2143
01:16:42,140 --> 01:16:44,319
[SPEAKER_00] najateističkija zemlja u Evropi.

2144
01:16:44,319 --> 01:16:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] I Halik kaže upravo to.

2145
01:16:46,159 --> 01:16:48,279
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan od glavnih razloga

2146
01:16:48,279 --> 01:16:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] opadanja vjera u Češkoj

2147
01:16:49,819 --> 01:16:50,899
[SPEAKER_00] je to što je crkva

2148
01:16:50,899 --> 01:16:52,560
[SPEAKER_00] bez izvanskog pritiska

2149
01:16:52,560 --> 01:16:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji su je nametnule

2150
01:16:54,039 --> 01:16:55,399
[SPEAKER_00] komunističke vlasti

2151
01:16:55,399 --> 01:16:57,560
[SPEAKER_00] ostala nesposobna ponuditi

2152
01:16:57,560 --> 01:16:59,060
[SPEAKER_00] nešto autentično svoje.

2153
01:16:59,060 --> 01:17:01,359
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva je svoj identitet

2154
01:17:01,359 --> 01:17:03,359
[SPEAKER_00] razvila u otporu prema svijetu.

2155
01:17:03,359 --> 01:17:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kad se kršćanska poruka

2156
01:17:05,619 --> 01:17:06,859
[SPEAKER_00] u demokratskom društvu

2157
01:17:06,859 --> 01:17:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] našla na otvorenom tržištu

2158
01:17:08,500 --> 01:17:09,840
[SPEAKER_00] na kojem se bori

2159
01:17:09,840 --> 01:17:10,979
[SPEAKER_00] s drugim porukama

2160
01:17:10,979 --> 01:17:13,079
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno nije znala

2161
01:17:13,079 --> 01:17:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] što niti kako ponuditi.

2162
01:17:14,800 --> 01:17:17,399
[SPEAKER_00] Od tada kao da postoji želja

2163
01:17:17,399 --> 01:17:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] da pronađemo nekog drugog

2164
01:17:19,119 --> 01:17:21,659
[SPEAKER_00] s kim ćemo se boriti

2165
01:17:21,659 --> 01:17:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] i od koga ćemo se oduprijeti

2166
01:17:23,500 --> 01:17:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] kako bismo sebi dali smisao postojanja.

2167
01:17:25,899 --> 01:17:28,720
[SPEAKER_00] A kada nema tog drugog

2168
01:17:28,720 --> 01:17:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] ili ga nema dovoljno

2169
01:17:29,880 --> 01:17:31,819
[SPEAKER_00] onda se potrudimo pronaći ga.

2170
01:17:31,819 --> 01:17:34,039
[SPEAKER_00] Takvo nas raspoloženje

2171
01:17:34,039 --> 01:17:35,939
[SPEAKER_00] dovodi do vitoperenja stvarnosti

2172
01:17:35,939 --> 01:17:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] i gubitka osjećaja za trenutak

2173
01:17:37,920 --> 01:17:39,020
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem se nalazimo

2174
01:17:39,020 --> 01:17:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] kako bismo u njemu znali

2175
01:17:40,800 --> 01:17:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] komunicirati kršćansku poruku.

2176
01:17:42,659 --> 01:17:44,699
[SPEAKER_00] To je vrlo veliki gubitak

2177
01:17:44,699 --> 01:17:46,979
[SPEAKER_00] jel pravi kršćanin treba uz nastojat

2178
01:17:46,979 --> 01:17:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] da može sa svijetim pavlom reći

2179
01:17:49,340 --> 01:17:50,699
[SPEAKER_00] svima bijak sve

2180
01:17:50,699 --> 01:17:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] ne bili pošto po to neke stekao.

2181
01:17:53,000 --> 01:17:54,739
[SPEAKER_00] I to je istina.

2182
01:17:54,739 --> 01:17:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] Danas je otvorena ponuda.

2183
01:17:56,119 --> 01:17:58,319
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je zanimljiv.

2184
01:17:58,319 --> 01:18:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mi se nismo snašli u tome

2185
01:18:01,039 --> 01:18:03,159
[SPEAKER_00] jer smo gradili svoj identitet

2186
01:18:03,159 --> 01:18:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] protiv drugih.

2187
01:18:04,220 --> 01:18:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] Protiv svijeta.

2188
01:18:06,199 --> 01:18:06,979
[SPEAKER_00] U negativi.

2189
01:18:06,979 --> 01:18:08,819
[SPEAKER_00] U defanzivi.

2190
01:18:10,819 --> 01:18:12,359
[SPEAKER_00] I zato smo neprivlačni.

2191
01:18:12,359 --> 01:18:15,739
[SPEAKER_00] Moramo promijeniti mentalitet.

2192
01:18:15,739 --> 01:18:17,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ako želimo

2193
01:18:17,100 --> 01:18:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] dovesti veći broj ljudi

2194
01:18:19,199 --> 01:18:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] kristu.

2195
01:18:19,880 --> 01:18:21,520
[SPEAKER_00] Pogotovo ako mlade ljude

2196
01:18:21,520 --> 01:18:22,819
[SPEAKER_00] danas želimo zapaliti.

2197
01:18:22,819 --> 01:18:24,340
[SPEAKER_00] Moramo mijenjati

2198
01:18:24,340 --> 01:18:25,340
[SPEAKER_00] taj mentalitet.

2199
01:18:28,340 --> 01:18:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je Billy Graham

2200
01:18:29,800 --> 01:18:31,939
[SPEAKER_00] pokretao na ABC-u

2201
01:18:31,939 --> 01:18:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] na glavnoj američkoj televiziji

2202
01:18:33,420 --> 01:18:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] program

2203
01:18:33,819 --> 01:18:34,260
[SPEAKER_00] ako je

2204
01:18:34,260 --> 01:18:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] religijski program

2205
01:18:35,420 --> 01:18:36,640
[SPEAKER_00] će biti dovoljno zanimljiv

2206
01:18:36,640 --> 01:18:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] za osam na večer.

2207
01:18:38,500 --> 01:18:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] Top termin.

2208
01:18:39,579 --> 01:18:42,279
[SPEAKER_00] Svi su mu rekli da je lud.

2209
01:18:42,279 --> 01:18:43,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je postala

2210
01:18:43,359 --> 01:18:44,600
[SPEAKER_00] najgledanija emisija.

2211
01:18:44,600 --> 01:18:46,640
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

2212
01:18:46,640 --> 01:18:48,060
[SPEAKER_00] Kad su ga pitali

2213
01:18:48,060 --> 01:18:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] kao odakle mu bila vjera za to.

2214
01:18:49,619 --> 01:18:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže pa sad to li sam znao

2215
01:18:51,380 --> 01:18:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] da je Bog zanimljiv.

2216
01:18:52,460 --> 01:18:54,659
[SPEAKER_00] Na nama je

2217
01:18:54,659 --> 01:18:55,899
[SPEAKER_00] očemo li ga mi prikazati

2218
01:18:55,899 --> 01:18:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] kakav je.

2219
01:18:56,460 --> 01:18:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] I zato

2220
01:18:57,659 --> 01:18:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] trebamo se

2221
01:18:59,159 --> 01:19:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] izvući iz te defanzive.

2222
01:19:00,659 --> 01:19:02,720
[SPEAKER_00] To su sve ostaci

2223
01:19:02,720 --> 01:19:04,380
[SPEAKER_00] komunističkog režima

2224
01:19:04,380 --> 01:19:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] koji su i dalje u nama.

2225
01:19:05,800 --> 01:19:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] I došlo je vrijeme

2226
01:19:07,619 --> 01:19:08,439
[SPEAKER_00] da se sa time

2227
01:19:08,439 --> 01:19:09,560
[SPEAKER_00] obračunamo.

2228
01:19:09,560 --> 01:19:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] Suparništva i senzacionalizmi

2229
01:19:11,659 --> 01:19:14,279
[SPEAKER_00] samo na kratko vrijeme

2230
01:19:14,279 --> 01:19:15,899
[SPEAKER_00] mogu prikriti

